The following percentages of quantities covered by import licence applications submitted in respect of the period 1 July to 31 December 2003 under the quotas referred to in Regulation (EC) No 1279/98 may be allowed:
(a) 100 % of quantities covered by applications in respect of products falling within CN codes 0201 and 0202 originating in Slovakia and the Czech Republic;
(b) 100 % of quantities covered by applications in respect of products falling within CN code 1602 50 originating in Romania;
(c) 0,32866 % of quantities covered by applications in respect of products falling within CN codes 0201, 0202 and 1602 50 10 originating in Poland;
(d) 87,02202 % of quantities covered by applications in respect of products falling within CN codes 0201 and 0202 originating in Hungary.
